SPORT: Six Nations Rugby Union - Italy v France
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Sunday 3rd February 2013 
KO Time: 15:00 

Live coverage from Rome as Italy meet France on the opening weekend of the 2013 Six Nations. The French began the 2012 campaign with a 30-12 victory over their continental neighbours, but went on to finish a disappointing fourth in the championship. Italy will be hoping for a repeat of the last time the two sides met in Rome in 2011, which ended in a memorable 22-21 victory for the Azzurri. Commentary by Alastair Eykyn and Jonathan Davies.
